data.body:
Most definitely polish but would allow some interesting use cases;
- (toggleable?) silent shell map but with music and UI noises. Imho the current shellmaps sounds can become annoying when waiting in the MP lobby. You can also miss lobby noises.
- ingame menus could silence ingame sounds and just play music and UI noises, which would be a nice touch at bringing you 'out of the action' temporarily when bring up the options during a live game.
